  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "CLASS 3 DRIVER",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a reliable and responsible <strong>Class 3  Driver</strong> to support our logistics and delivery operations . The successful candidate will be responsible for transporting goods safely and efficiently while ensuring compliance with company procedures and road safety regulations.</p><h3><u><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></u></h3><ul><li>Perform delivery and collection of goods to customers, warehouses, and distribution points</li></ul><ul><li> Ensure timely and accurate delivery according to assigned schedules and routes</li></ul><ul><li>Load and unload goods safely, ensuring proper handling and protection</li></ul><ul><li> Conduct daily checks on vehicle condition and report any defects promptly</li></ul><ul><li> Maintain cleanliness and proper care of the assigned company vehicle</li></ul><ul><li> Prepare, verify, and submit delivery orders and related documentation</li></ul><ul><li> Adhere to traffic laws, workplace safety standards, and company policies</li></ul><ul><li> Coordinate with operations and warehouse teams to ensure smooth logistics flow</li></ul><ul><li> Perform other logistics-related duties as assigned</li></ul><h3><u><strong>Qualifications & Experience:</strong></u></h3><ul><li> Possess a valid <strong>Singapore Class 3 Driving License</strong></li></ul><ul><li> Minimum 3-4<strong> year of relevant driving or logistics experience</strong> preferred</li></ul><ul><li> Familiar with Singapore road networks and delivery routes</li></ul><ul><li> Must be Singaporean or PR or Service Sector Pass holder</li></ul><ul><li> Basic understanding of logistics operations and documentation</li></ul><ul><li> Physically fit and able to perform loading and unloading tasks</li></ul><ul><li> Responsible, punctual, and safety-conscious</li><li> Able to communicate in basic English</li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
